{"tid":690982,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 新作三分日本? 三極正義 三極ジャスティス","createTime":"2018-06-05T09:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T13:27:31.000Z","uid":75453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5c87a5f870045c587d01076bbad077cb22a7a3","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"《三極正義》世界觀<br />\n <br />\n　　2038 年。日本因為少子化與人口減少的關係而解禁了生命科學相關研究，想要透過工廠來量產出優良的國民，取回失去的榮耀。<br />\n <br />\n　　這項措施受到周圍國家的強力反對，並支援反政府勢力，於是日本的內戰就開始了。<br />\n <br />\n　　2040 年。雙方都陷入了看不見未來的疲態，也出現了新的國際犯罪組織勢力。<br />\n <br />\n　　主張「強悍日本」的政府組織、反對政府的反政府勢力、趁亂而入的國際犯罪集團，這 3 個勢力的爭奪讓事態變得更加混亂，日本看不見未來的內戰不知要持續到何時。<br />\n <br />\n　　可無限製造人類的世界讓戰線呈現膠著狀態，也沒有人會感嘆死亡了。3 個勢力一步步邁向不存在的日本未來。<br />\n <br />\n《三極正義》角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8Ir7EvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8Ir7EvQ.jpg&h=9316ea5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　本作中的三方勢力分為：提倡以優秀的頭腦來領導國民，企圖以武力來統治的「霞關」；喊出取回和平日本口號的「諸神」；製造兵器、從事戰爭生意，企圖統治日本經濟的「達克西斯」。這次公開了各領導人與副手角色。<br />\n<br />\n標榜「支配」的霞之關（カスミガセキ）的領導者京極晴也──CV杉田智和<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K4cb7J3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK4cb7J3.jpg&h=cee3716a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n標榜「自由」的八百萬（ヤオヨロズ）的領導者神室友美──CV植田佳奈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CZeLrqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCZeLrqO.jpg&h=1d70aeb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n標榜「金欲」的黑暗姊妹（ダクシス）的領導者破滅之人形（破滅の人形）──CV內田彩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/34KEb6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F34KEb6L.jpg&h=9a9515ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G7wmcSz-Jt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG7wmcSz-Jt0&d=X3RJmpT%2FhfxEqYimeumNsk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9b72dbfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G7wmcSz-Jt0</a><br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://3jus.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3jus.jp%2F&d=X3RJmpT%2FhfxEqYimeumNsk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2e8ebc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://3jus.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n勢力選錯會問你2次,之後選錯左就唔係改返,請小心<br />\n暫時第一戰 紅&gt;藍&gt;綠<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AmJGWsW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAmJGWsW.jpg&h=e74c882c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eba1f98d7954eb541ad64dd38a6b3805401917c","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"暫時係紅國刷緊首抽<br />\n首抽total 15下<br />\n教學5下(中到SSR但難D)+教學完左去抽卡到有10下無料事前10抽送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bac856129196f07495ef34e7b1351f322edef20","tid":690982,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"好似幾有趣"},{"pid":"968407a15eb479fd4077fc6acff786a03924b206","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c84e96f61ecc230c9c9fdf973d4ecf71443cfb7","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcee9a1b0d91a0ffd68172a6634eda7932ebb28","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"冇人岩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21289f12ff0a4af54d6425a862192762127edfd5","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee5f6d87196d0ec49c666df3e66db56be3ffe9","tid":690982,"uid":75453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-